  "description": "<p>When after-dark adventures happen, this mega-bright and feature-rich headlamp lights the way. The Spot 400's touch-sensitive activation allows you to get to the brightest setting with the tap of your finger. On rainy or snowy evening trail runs, rugged waterproofing ensures your path ahead stays illuminated.</p><ul><li>PowerTap\u2122 feature on the housing takes you from any brightness mode to full power with a single tap. Tap it again to return lighting level</li><li>6 modes include bright white proximity, bright white distance, dimming, strobe, red proximity and red strobe</li><li>Intuitive 2-button controls give you easy access to red lighting and flipping between spot and flood lighting</li><li>Night-vision friendly red light can be activated without cycling through white lighting</li><li>3-level power meter gives you an idea of how much juice is left</li><li>Lockout feature protects against accidental activations</li><li>Compatible with 3 AAA batteries (included) or rechargeable BD 1500 Li-ion battery (sold separately)</li></ul>",
